HEADWORD: Trichinous
<hw>Trich"i*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining
to trichinae or trichinosis; affected with, or containing, trichinae;
<as>as, <ex>trichinous</ex> meat</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

